To make package:
-After building copy Komodo-qt from src/qt to content folder and rename to action-qt-mac 
-compress content of "content" folder in zip file.

To install:
-Extract the archive, then open a terminal window, and use the script to download the z-cash parameters by typing
./fetch-params.sh

-Once the download is complete, open the file named "action.conf" in a text editor and change the values for "rpcuser" and "rpcpassword" to some other values, save the file and close it. There is no need to remember these values.

-Now, run the following command in the Terminal to create a directory named "Action" in your "Application Support" directory and move the file "action.conf" to it.
mkdir -p ~/Library/Application\ Support/Action && cp action.conf ~/Library/Application\ Support/Action

-After that, open the file named action-qt-mac in the package directory